spell_list.description: The bruiser leaps to their ally if they're outside of 10 meters and intercedes for them for a short duration. All non-fighters near the leap target will reduce their hate position with nearby enemies. This spell can be toggled off early.
spell_list.description_pvp: The bruiser leaps to their ally if they're outside of 10 meters and intercedes for them for a short duration. All non-fighters near the leap target will reduce their hate position with nearby enemies. This spell can be toggled off early.

effect_list.description: Reduces the threat position of all non-fighters within 10 meters of the target by 1 with all targets in the area.  In PVP combat, this makes all non-fighter allies close to the target invalid targets for enemy attacks for 0.5 seconds.
100% chance to intercept all damage on target.On a successful intercept caster takes 25% of attack damage, target takes 25% of attack damage.
Instantly teleport to your target if you're 10 meters away
